@startuml approach2-detailed-activity
title **Approach 2: InMemoryCosmosClient + InMemoryContainer — Query Flow (Detailed)**

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam ActivityBorderColor #333
skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor #E8F4FD
skinparam PartitionBorderColor #666

|Test Code|
start
:Call **InMemoryCosmosClient.GetContainer**
(databaseId, containerId);

|InMemoryCosmosClient|
:**_databases.GetOrAdd**(databaseId, …)
→ ConcurrentDictionary lookup
→ thread-safe lazy creation;

if (database exists?) then (yes)
  :Return existing **InMemoryDatabase**;
else (no)
  :Create **new InMemoryDatabase**
  (databaseId, client);
endif

|InMemoryDatabase|
:**GetOrCreateContainer**
(containerId, partitionKeyPath);

:**_containers.GetOrAdd**(containerId, …)
→ ConcurrentDictionary lookup
→ thread-safe lazy creation;

if (container exists?) then (yes)
  :Return existing **InMemoryContainer**;
else (no)
  :Create **new InMemoryContainer**
  (containerId, partitionKeyPath);
endif

note right
  Subsequent GetContainer() calls with
  same databaseId + containerId return
  the **SAME instance** — data is shared
  across all callers.
end note

|Test Code|
:Receive Container (InMemoryContainer);

#LightGreen:=== SQL Query Flow ===
(identical to Approach 1)|

|InMemoryContainer|
:Call **GetItemQueryIterator<T>**
(queryText, continuationToken, requestOptions);

:Call **FilterItemsByQuery**
(queryText, parameters, requestOptions);

|CosmosSqlParser|
:**Parse**(queryText)
→ CosmosSqlQuery AST
(SelectFields, Where, OrderBy,
GroupBy, Distinct, Top, Offset, Limit);

|InMemoryContainer.FilterItemsByQuery|
:**GetAllItemsForPartition**(requestOptions)
→ List<string> from ConcurrentDictionary
→ partition key filtering, TTL exclusion;

:**AugmentWithComputedProperties**();

:**ExpandFromSource**()
→ FROM c IN c.arrayField;

:**ExpandAllJoins**()
→ JOIN array flattening;

#LightYellow:=== WHERE per item ===
**EvaluateWhereExpression**
→ **EvaluateSqlExpression** (recursive)
→ all expression types:
Literal, Identifier, PropertyAccess,
IndexAccess, Binary, Unary, FunctionCall
(40+ functions), Between, In, Like,
Ternary, Coalesce, Subquery,
ArrayLiteral, ObjectLiteral|

:**ApplyGroupBy**() + aggregates
(COUNT, SUM, AVG, MIN, MAX);

:**ApplyOrderByFields**()
→ multi-field, ASC/DESC;

:Apply **TOP** / **OFFSET+LIMIT**;

:**ProjectFields**()
→ SELECT projection;

:**StripComputedProperties**();

:Apply **DISTINCT**;

:**UnwrapValueSelect**()
→ SELECT VALUE;

:Return List<string> (JSON);

|InMemoryContainer|
:Deserialize → List<T>;
:Create **InMemoryFeedIterator<T>**;

|Test Code|
while (HasMoreResults?) is (yes)
  :ReadNextAsync();

  |InMemoryFeedIterator<T>|
  :EnsureItems() → Paginate
  → Skip(offset).Take(maxItemCount)
  → continuation token
  → **InMemoryFeedResponse<T>**;

  |Test Code|
  :Receive **FeedResponse<T>**;

endwhile (no)

#LightBlue:=== LINQ Flow (also identical to Approach 1) ===|

note right
  GetItemLinqQueryable<T>()
  → GetAllItemsForPartition()
  → Deserialize → .AsQueryable().OrderBy(x => 0)
  → **IOrderedQueryable<T>** (LINQ-to-Objects)
  → User applies .Where() / .Select() / .OrderBy()
  → .ToFeedIteratorOverridable()
  → InMemoryFeedIteratorSetup.CreateInMemoryFeedIterator<T>()
  → InMemoryFeedIterator<T>
  → ReadNextAsync() → InMemoryFeedResponse<T>
end note

stop

@enduml
